 Python program to find the sum of the series: 1 -4 +9 -16 +25 â€¦. till the given number N.

n=int(input("Enter the value of N: "))
sumn=0
for i in range(1,n+1):
    square=i*i
    if i%2 !=0:
        sumn += square
    else:
        sumn -= square
print(f"The sum of the series till {n} terms is: {sumn}")
